replies.body:
Besides the fact _your entire log -- as short as it may be -- is entirely made up of negativity and harassment_;

**You also are lucky to get away with a 2-week ban as a first offense instead of a permaban** due to hate speech, which is normally permaban worthy (zero tolerance 'rule').

I'm surprised Riot hasn't decided to escalate it to a perma already, especially since you told someone to "kill themselves" _as well as_ whatever the %%% hate speech word was.
